 문서 발행</p></li></ul><p local-id=\"944ada66-83e7-4dbb-9a3c-b4c925f50270\">&nbsp;</p><h1 local-id=\"0605ed99-7afd-42c1-9f92-1e28080ba350\">가이드 및 스펙확인</h1><ac:structured-macro ac:name=\"info\" ac:schema-version=\"1\" ac:local-id=\"c4ef83d9-9850-49be-8ed3-93e4e96fdeb5\" ac:macro-id=\"2a8cc744-9b0d-448e-b3ff-054419683f94\"><ac:rich-text-body><p local-id=\"28d6f2e5-14b8-402c-a0e1-94a3892f77db\">자세한 스펙은 아래 링크로 확인 가능합니다.</p><ul local-id=\"e3257122-beca-4304-87d6-88fcd20ef26b\"><li local-id=\"a192956b-8069-4781-af34-ee94e41d27c7\"><p local-id=\"cd18fa1a-6032-4d98-8387-1dca11e785df\"><ac:emoticon ac:name=\"blue-star\" ac:emoji-shortname=\":figma:\" ac:emoji-id=\"c1fabecb-6925-40a3-9b8b-4f32041bb854\" ac:local-id=\"504a877f-35ab-42c9-b15d-83f54c121057\" ac:emoji-fallback=\":figma:\" /> <a href=\"https://www.figma.com/design/c8Qux8CARpdsaKg1KsUwMm/branch/kTqJKoIogkmdRAzIdqIQWI/-%EA%B3%B5%ED%86%B5--ORDO-Design-system?m=auto&amp;node-id=53011-16452&amp;t=2p511ysl7TB23Xpe-1\"><strong><u>Sub Category 피그마 링크</u></strong></a></p></li><li local-id=\"3c0ec5c1-b2c1-41d2-89d9-c34e41236fda\"><p local-id=\"df203f63-919f-424e-8a8e-fcdbc722feec\"><ac:emoticon ac:name=\"link\" ac:emoji-shortname=\":link:\" ac:emoji-id=\"1f517\" ac:local-id=\"abc0377f-9a7d-43db-b5fc-ac30a0fe271c\" ac:emoji-fallback=\"\uD83D\uDD17\" /> <a href=\"https://ordo.pubg.io/?path=/story/functional-time-indicator--time-indicator\"><strong><u>PUBG ID Storybook</u></strong></a><strong> (등록후 변경 필요)</strong></p></li></ul></ac:rich-text-body></ac:structured-macro><h1 local-id=\"d267dccc-3072-480f-9a3b-bb707a730269\"><br />정의</h1><p local-id=\"c4660cb8-f72c-47d4-83a7-546eac467384\"><ac:structured-macro ac:name=\"status\" ac:schema-version=\"1\" ac:macro-id=\"5980cb82-f58f-4112-91ca-badd4b0cd64d\"><ac:parameter ac:name=\"title\">complex</ac:parameter><ac:parameter ac:name=\"colour\">Yellow</ac:parameter></ac:structured-macro>  서브 카테고리 기능을 제공하기 위한 <strong>태그 형태의 버튼 UI</strong>로, 사용자는 해당 버튼을 통해 하위 카테고리를 선택하거나 해제할 수 있습니다. 각 태그 버튼은 독립적인 선택 상태를 가지며, 카테고리 탐색을 보조하는 보조 필터 역할로 사용됩니다.</p><ac:image ac:align=\"center\" ac:layout=\"center\" ac:original-height=\"378\" ac:original-width=\"635\" ac:custom-width=\"true\" ac:local-id=\"9afc8da8-574d-402f-b123-dd05e2f237fd\" ac:alt=\"서브카테고리 정의.png\" ac:width=\"507\"><ri:attachment ri:filename=\"서브카테고리 정의.png\" ri:version-at-save=\"1\" /></ac:image><p local-id=\"36fd88c9-3491-44ab-8320-a31e3164225b\">&nbsp;</p><h1 local-id=\"559c5242-580a-489c-aa35-f1719b898d40\">개발 사양</h1><h2 local-id=\"f9b9f0f9-7665-424a-88d4-8dd6a2131339\">속성별 규칙</h2><table data-table-width=\"760\" data-layout=\"default\" ac:local-id=\"1356070a-6e56-40c2-84e3-cb95cf3db721\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 116.0px;\" /><col style=\"width: 170.0px;\" /><col style=\"width: 473.0px;\" /></colgroup><tbody><tr ac:local-id=\"4a117f04-6c60-40cf-a83a-222b986d04bb\"><th ac:local-id=\"64b68748-18dd-4ffe-9a23-1a5d0eeec032\"><p local-id=\"df552906-7236-4cdb-924f-aee04bc3d71a\"><strong>속성</strong></p></th><th ac:local-id=\"7eeb6d4d-7b80-499a-af8a-f392f4857112\"><p local-id=\"2b288c8a-a550-438e-b5c7-63d966e0754e\"><strong>분류</strong></p></th><th ac:local-id=\"0b52a8ce-c333-429d-84f4-0d0f69d84697\"><p local-id=\"5e2a33d1-7f00-4b07-9c9a-6889be68c1cd\"><strong>규칙</strong></p></th></tr><tr ac:local-id=\"61c66634-94f0-4e5e-8deb-951bc97b9b13\"><td ac:local-id=\"c8f6a097-af0a-44cf-8e16-c41226f06653\"><p local-id=\"987d1ac0-a4d1-4349-abf9-23e880a02bbb\">서브카테고리 상태</p></td><td ac:local-id=\"5a2ff4df-4c67-48de-be36-c8bdf7324c43\"><ul local-id=\"2321446b-d928-4b0d-90cb-df930b366e8c\"><li local-id=\"69a56d5e-9f91-4093-a921-b1767edf1295\"><p local-id=\"27a3ab12-aecd-4a99-9a06-2d505e633dde\">Normal <ac:structured-macro ac:name=\"status\" ac:schema-version=\"1\" ac:macro-id=\"928110e5-a1ea-4dfd-a68e-7170028e3c9f\"><ac:parameter ac:name=\"title\">default</ac:parameter><ac:parameter ac:name=\"colour\">Green</ac:parameter></ac:structured-macro></p></li><li local-id=\"aef535d7-e5b2-49cd-a877-2d213a2d5d4f\"><p local-id=\"b4936a5b-316b-4c16-a019-e014a4fcfc11\">Hover</p></li><li local-id=\"4d83ba35-083f-4f25-8ca2-f147809c4fc1\"><p local-id=\"2cf7256b-c676-4273-a9cb-6e603e1699b4\">Active</p></li><li local-id=\"365fc259-9736-4a15-a23b-5308b04f4a30\"><p local-id=\"15eb0ede-3eaf-4a9f-8bdf-11607fa16c31\">Inactive(<ac:inline-comment-marker ac:ref=\"a95d791b-64c0-4cf3-b76f-161e2c2fb430\">무기참에서 사용</ac:inline-comment-marker>)</p></li></ul></td><td ac:local-id=\"9eba3d74-a7e4-47db-bff0-535447237fba\"><ac:image ac:align=\"center\" ac:layout=\"center\" ac:original-height=\"378\" ac:original-width=\"635\" ac:custom-width=\"true\" ac:local-id=\"4a828367db4f\" ac:alt=\"서브카테고리 프로퍼티.png\" ac:width=\"457\"><ri:attachment ri:filename=\"서브카테고리 프로퍼티.png\" ri:version-at-save=\"4\" /></ac:image><table data-table-width=\"760\" data-layout=\"default\" ac:local-id=\"06190636-f8f8-42c8-a9cb-99fa01380d8a\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 104.0px;\" /><col style=\"width: 352.0px;\" /></colgroup><tbody><tr ac:local-id=\"07154860-57ab-48ac-a58f-114473400244\"><th ac:local-id=\"178a1a5f-9e0b-48a2-82a7-9e80d7a32f69\"><p local-id=\"212328bd-8f70-4667-a13a-027129778ddd\">상태명</p></th><th ac:local-id=\"fe84ae47-a565-4e73-b665-ef275b7e217d\"><p local-id=\"bf90c7a5-a3aa-44bf-ba48-ba416063681a\">설명</p></th></tr><tr ac:local-id=\"5f95ce89-b573-40af-99cf-ff5267fa021b\"><td ac:local-id=\"9113bb56-e2c6-4331-bcd2-35ec5e193dab\"><p local-id=\"c2904eb8-8530-49a4-b696-703e479cc573\"><strong>Normal</strong></p></td><td ac:local-id=\"4a8b18f6-6734-4e51-b71b-6187f1cbc1f6\"><p local-id=\"e7d019fd-413c-4fcc-b8ef-b6468192230c\">서브카테고리의 기본 상태로, 별도의 배경 강조 없이 기본 문구 스타일이 노출됨.</p></td></tr><tr ac:local-id=\"4f1b8f2b-fa4f-4380-bfc9-d58be9b97c06\"><td ac:local-id=\"7a1bb131-5cad-4cea-9328-2ef655b0c9c0\"><p local-id=\"f139286c-a1dd-44ee-9c08-ca55ebf36bc9\"><strong>Hover</strong></p></td><td ac:local-id=\"5a7bfa1e-6c91-40a1-ab3b-aefad73ddf43\"><p local-id=\"bf493a7b-9ef0-4cdd-875f-4c8d63007bd0\">서브카테고리에 마우스를 올렸을 때의 상태로, 회색 배경이 노출되며 내부 문구 색상이 검정색으로 반전됨.</p></td></tr><tr ac:local-id=\"72702d85-3e55-4a33-a4f1-578fd62c148b\"><td ac:local-id=\"3758b9c3-3a34-4578-9e15-a33906485433\"><p local-id=\"a1a0603c-492a-4023-b15a-6deb44cf4e00\"><strong>Active</strong></p></td><td ac:local-id=\"96541f08-d13c-4827-8fbe-c062365318e1\"><p local-id=\"ccf644a7-df24-4f18-bf73-5bdde25bf46c\">서브카테고리를 선택하여 활성화된 상태로, 투명한 그라데이션 배경이 노출되어 선택 상태를 강조함.</p></td></tr><tr ac:local-id=\"462457e2-eeb3-412b-93dd-5ef62829deb8\"><td ac:local-id=\"84b05571-c4bc-4f8f-9047-cd2a00db13bc\"><p local-id=\"3ae72601-b8d6-4a04-a6da-d6bde37e6b6c\"><strong>Inactive</strong></p></td><td ac:local-id=\"328c755a-7cea-4d25-9795-a30fc00aa897\"><p local-id=\"e39838f5-f8b3-4cac-a57f-62f1eff6a9fa\">서브카테고리가 비활성화된 상태로, 내부 문구의 Opacity가 Normal 대비 50%로 감소하며, 호버 및 선택 인터랙션이 비활성화됨</p></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr><tr ac:local-id=\"4d5259705aa1\"><td ac:local-id=\"3a7f9354b327\"><p local-id=\"f5eee4ee9e3f\">내부 정보 표기 방식</p></td><td ac:local-id=\"cb904bf23d01\"><ul local-id=\"b63d904fd18a\"><li local-id=\"c52502321bea\"><p local-id=\"90c1b7df698d\">텍스트 <ac:structured-macro ac:name=\"status\" ac:schema-version=\"1\" ac:macro-id=\"233f9c81-585f-4bb6-ae9f-3fa4f14ca5d8\"><ac:parameter ac:name=\"title\">default</ac:parameter><ac:parameter ac:name=\"colour\">Green</ac:parameter></ac:structured-macro>  </p></li><li local-id=\"3d2333ba6d01\"><p local-id=\"2910729696dc\">아이콘+텍스트</p></li><li local-id=\"5ef0622efe80\"><p local-id=\"27dcdd43800e\">아이콘</p></li></ul></td><td ac:local-id=\"094475a1f725\"><ac:image ac:align=\"center\" ac:layout=\"center\" ac:original-height=\"378\" ac:original-width=\"635\" ac:custom-width=\"true\" ac:local-id=\"c20c67ea65ad\" ac:alt=\"내부 정보 표기 방식.png\" ac:width=\"457\"><ri:attachment ri:filename=\"내부 정보 표기 방식.png\" ri:version-at-save=\"2\" /></ac:image><table data-table-width=\"760\" data-layout=\"default\" ac:local-id=\"659a8715-c812-4301-a81d-820acc2c4510\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 112.0px;\" /><col style=\"width: 344.0px;\" /></colgroup><tbody><tr ac:local-id=\"8ffe692b6b04\"><th ac:local-id=\"32c92f79-235c-41eb-bbd4-eb1c294e2363\"><p local-id=\"f2894906b51e\"><strong>상태명</strong></p></th><th ac:local-id=\"d55110f6-1e3f-44df-8323-b52fd097fdb0\"><p local-id=\"506b5016f396\"><strong>설명</strong></p></th></tr><tr ac:local-id=\"60f70b65e5c4\"><td ac:local-id=\"a04cc3da-412f-42c4-a335-2f476fa4112e\"><p local-id=\"9f2a53358d8a\">텍스트</p></td><td ac:local-id=\"13989c12-e103-45a9-a7b7-b16f694272b0\"><p local-id=\"27546caf12f6\">컴포넌트 내부에 텍스트만 보여주는 방식</p></td></tr><tr ac:local-id=\"757e97537c26\"><td ac:local-id=\"4da743ad-b737-40ac-92dd-59a3577522f8\"><p local-id=\"8526ff3c0ae4\">아이콘 + 텍스트</p></td><td ac:local-id=\"8342016a-f34f-48c3-b0f5-68fe6a9d6384\"><p local-id=\"8e9990f954a4\">컴포넌트 내부에 텍스트와 아이콘을 함께 표기하며, 아이콘은 텍스트 앞에 위치함. 아이콘 종류에는 제한이 없으며 어떤 아이콘이든 사용 가능</p></td></tr><tr ac:local-id=\"dbeff75ab17b\"><td ac:local-id=\"9e706c1a-3719-4094-8981-ca7a049f37b0\"><p local-id=\"4abc445531e7\">아이콘</p></td><td ac:local-id=\"639d5666-e740-4e0f-a1c0-3655113fe69f\"><p local-id=\"a65f86fdc07f\">컴포넌트 내부에 아이콘만 보여주는 방식</p></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr><tr ac:local-id=\"b2db45bf-f3ec-45b8-b9eb-69a769289a91\"><td ac:local-id=\"8f60ce27-e977-47d3-83cc-06437bed9778\"><p local-id=\"342a5fef-09b6-41f1-a828-42050d2ad88d\">태그 버튼 수량 규칙</p></td><td ac:local-id=\"f496cd7d-4fe2-4bc5-b760-3f6513ee8fc7\"><ul local-id=\"ba3d7f3a-bd28-4b76-b223-bc65ccd7f28c\"><li local-id=\"0c6faab7-0e0d-479f-9470-5eb6c0e84805\"><p local-id=\"c9c8044f-c7b7-4753-be2f-cf47f1ebfe9b\"><ac:inline-comment-marker ac:ref=\"4d1db632-a2d1-44d7-b232-6ce749ef3fd8\">최소 2개이상</ac:inline-comment-marker> <ac:structured-macro ac:name=\"status\" ac:schema-version=\"1\" ac:macro-id=\"ab39f41e-67e3-4d4e-81db-aa89e802ad21\"><ac:parameter ac:name=\"title\">default</ac:parameter><ac:parameter ac:name=\"colour\">Green</ac:parameter></ac:structured-macro>  </p></li></ul></td><td ac:local-id=\"6a00f31a-76b9-4c31-9aab-692ef24e3667\"><ac:image ac:align=\"center\" ac:layout=\"center\" ac:original-height=\"662\" ac:original-width=\"956\" ac:custom-width=\"true\" ac:local-id=\"d39877fd577c\" ac:alt=\"태그버튼 수량 규칙.png\" ac:width=\"457\"><ri:attachment ri:filename=\"태그버튼 수량 규칙.png\" ri:version-at-save=\"3\" /></ac:image><ul local-id=\"83564a56-af6d-4b8d-9266-91f40218643a\"><li local-id=\"f5f5c904-58ee-4469-8816-914a0b6f25b6\"><p local-id=\"3c692ccf-8cbf-4c88-be58-d1dd63a61043\">서브카테고리는 최소 2개 이상 노출되어야 합니다.</p></li><li local-id=\"77e94d5518f6\"><p local-id=\"d0d5cd13046c\">지정된 최대 수량 제한은 없고, 각 피쳐에서 디자인에 따라 지정된 width값에 따라 컴포넌트들이 줄바꿈 처리된다</p></li></ul></td></tr><tr ac:local-id=\"cecb3ed8-c53c-475c-bf18-940c3908368c\"><td ac:local-id=\"5b18a54e-0452-45ee-b511-a7fa5ab8c327\"><p local-id=\"6d09cadf-1ff0-4fef-99bf-a47634d723d8\">단일/복수 선택 여부</p></td><td ac:local-id=\"0e83a632-55b1-4f43-83ff-25d1ef3fcfd1\"><ul local-id=\"7a3ad484-ff71-4fb9-b7c0-c705facaa95b\"><li local-id=\"7a0359c2-c58b-4498-8f20-f167846c9f84\"><p local-id=\"9ba4b967-9000-4c13-be76-625fb440b59f\">단일 선택 <ac:structured-macro ac:name=\"status\" ac:schema-version=\"1\" ac:macro-id=\"5def259f-abfd-444d-be20-0f47ecfc7316\"><ac:parameter ac:name=\"title\">default</ac:parameter><ac:parameter ac:name=\"colour\">Green</ac:parameter></ac:structured-macro>  </p></li></ul></td><td ac:local-id=\"1fe8eb1b-2b3d-47f9-b041-25a9c7af8ab2\"><ac:image ac:align=\"center\" ac:layout=\"center\" ac:original-height=\"679\" ac:original-width=\"1361\" ac:custom-width=\"true\" ac:local-id=\"168ce8fb05ed\" ac:alt=\"단일선택.png\" ac:width=\"457\"><ri:attachment ri:filename=\"단일선택.png\" ri:version-at-save=\"2\" /></ac:image><ul local-id=\"2ceacdce-5bbe-413f-bdb0-6f76e2229851\"><li local-id=\"ed6880e0-5c26-4f8f-9483-a4b63a6b300c\"><p local-id=\"ffbebf72-c5bd-4c6e-bd32-45ea536c0866\">서브카테고리는 단일 선택만 가능하고 복수 선택 불가</p></li></ul></td></tr><tr ac:local-id=\"354c2c16-2aaa-4450-a1a7-ce5ae5c89aed\"><td ac:local-id=\"3c524b96-9152-451a-95c5-76d00a12f016\"><p local-id=\"b1895879-e622-4cda-81e7-c9bacc367e31\">Divider 노출 규칙</p></td><td ac:local-id=\"4